@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.98) * tmp) - ((v0 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.33) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.21)))
    v1 = 0.28
    v1 = (0.26 + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.91) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.29)))
    tmp = (0.23 / wp.abs((v1 + 0.05 - tmp + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
